SCP 5334 idea


09 Jan 2021 10:06






My idea is to make a twist on the traditional story of the monster under the bed. SCP-5334 will be a medium size creature with a elongated face. SCP-5334 appears to be cut in half but shows not signs of bleeding, SCP-5334 walks around on it two drills it has for arms. When SCP-5334 finds a bed/any type of sleeping thing elevated above the ground at least 30cm by 8cm holes in the lower chest. It will then proceed by eating the Heart and organs of SCP-5334-1 before proceeding to the next victim.

This is a small description of the scp, i hope you can get back to me with thing i can change or make better.





